@node Overview
@chapter Overview

@samp{profiler-extras.el} extends the built-in Emacs profiler (@samp{profiler.el}) with convenience commands that reduce the number of steps needed for common profiling workflows. The standard profiler requires separate invocations to start, stop, and generate a report. This package provides a single toggle command that manages the entire cycle, as well as a command for quickly expanding all sub-entries in a profiler report.

The package requires only the built-in @samp{profiler} library.

